    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/388869c4c99dbb894df7e0831541fd67.avif?t=1759258940\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A third-person survival horror game. The story follows a girl with psychic power who tries to escape a secret laboratory swarming with grotesque and monstrous creatures. Uncover the truth behind the incident and embark on a thrilling adventure that'll keep you on the edge. Explore a sci-fi setting filled with mystery and danger, where a terror is waiting to attack you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/9d39da558592b7b0e11d513c8ed22025.avif?t=1759258940\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/bb268ee861b631b0329ba200ae639f2e.poster.avif?t=1759258940\" width=1170 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/bb268ee861b631b0329ba200ae639f2e.webm?t=1759258940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/bb268ee861b631b0329ba200ae639f2e.mp4?t=1759258940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You play as Elixia, a mysterious girl with unique psychic powers useful in combat and puzzle-solving. Wield a variety of psychic abilities to survive and overcome challenges. Unleash a forceful blast with the power of a bullet, use telekinesis to manipulate and hurl objects at high speed, cause enemies to implode under immense pressure, and create barriers to block and counter attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/fb4f490ed0f1adb4480a1c3771475503.avif?t=1759258940\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/b61944f339b88c777030a652bc78beee.poster.avif?t=1759258940\" width=1170 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/b61944f339b88c777030a652bc78beee.webm?t=1759258940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/b61944f339b88c777030a652bc78beee.mp4?t=1759258940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Face off against dreadful stalkers—twisted creations born from sinister experiments. These relentless creatures possess unique abilities, making them formidable foes who will stop at nothing to hunt you down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/2d8a98ad60bed345e381a9859ee4339a.avif?t=1759258940\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/ea8af9ee7315c3b9f9a7a70f89fb8d38.poster.avif?t=1759258940\" width=1170 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/ea8af9ee7315c3b9f9a7a70f89fb8d38.webm?t=1759258940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018390/extras/ea8af9ee7315c3b9f9a7a70f89fb8d38.mp4?t=1759258940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Experience a fresh take on survival horror that blends classic mechanics like limited resources, backtracking, and puzzle-solving with a dynamic environment, allowing you to adapt and respond to any situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Forge your own path to survival—whether through intense combat or stealthy evasion. Navigate and interact with a mysterious sci-fi laboratory, exploring freely as you uncover its dangers and secrets.</p>",
